27
00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:38.290
Remnants

28
00:01:35.370 --> 00:01:38.290
Got it, Perospero?

29
00:01:38.290 --> 00:01:43.250
Entering an alliance with
Kaido was my decision.

30
00:01:43.250 --> 00:01:45.290
Be that as it may,

31
00:01:45.290 --> 00:01:50.380
your family has long dreamed of the day
that you become the Pirate King, Mama!

32
00:01:50.380 --> 00:01:51.840
Lick!

33
00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:55.600
I know that, of course.

34
00:01:55.600 --> 00:01:59.390
Can't you all just trust me on this?

35
00:02:00.930 --> 00:02:02.310
Okay...

36
00:02:02.310 --> 00:02:04.190
Well, that's a relief.

37
00:02:06.150 --> 00:02:07.520
I see.

38
00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:14.360
I suppose this means our ogre-hunting party
has officially disbanded, Perospero?

39
00:02:14.910 --> 00:02:17.740
Even though I accepted your offer.

40
00:02:17.740 --> 00:02:19.200
Marco!

41
00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:21.330
I can't believe you're helping those punks.

42
00:02:21.330 --> 00:02:23.960
I thought better of you.

43
00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:28.670
The remnants of Whitebeard's crew
must truly be lost without their captain.

44
00:02:29.550 --> 00:02:34.380
I don't think you know what
"remnant" truly means, Big Mom!

45
00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:38.430
Do you really think...

46
00:02:44.390 --> 00:02:48.400
we're still bound to Pops' will?

47
00:02:49.480 --> 00:02:51.440
Those of us left behind...

48
00:02:52.190 --> 00:02:54.360
are free!

49
00:02:54.900 --> 00:02:58.700
True... dead men give no orders.

50
00:02:58.700 --> 00:03:00.620
You're free to act out.

51
00:03:01.290 --> 00:03:03.710
That's not quite it...

52
00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:08.630
I'm free to do whatever I want!

53
00:03:20.510 --> 00:03:22.470
I knew it was him!

54
00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:27.190
Carrot! Where are you going?!

55
00:03:27.190 --> 00:03:29.270
He was there! Pedro's killer!

56
00:03:31.270 --> 00:03:33.570
Now's your chance, Straw Hat! Go!

57
00:03:33.940 --> 00:03:34.940
Thanks!

58
00:03:36.780 --> 00:03:39.700
Banquet

Hall



Inside

the Castle

59
00:03:40.320 --> 00:03:41.910
The whole island is in chaos.

60
00:03:43.410 --> 00:03:45.580
Are they gonna come all the way up here?

61
00:03:45.580 --> 00:03:48.040
I can't believe no one's
here in the tatami room!

62
00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:51.130
Would you sing us a song, Big Sis Maria?

63
00:03:51.500 --> 00:03:52.630
All right.

64
00:03:53.250 --> 00:03:56.050
How about this?

65
00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:02.890
♪ On a snowy night... ♪

66
00:04:04.310 --> 00:04:06.140
Wait!

67
00:04:08.270 --> 00:04:11.190
♪ ...two yearning lovers... ♪

68
00:04:12.940 --> 00:04:15.690
♪ kept apart by fate... ♪

69
00:04:17.860 --> 00:04:20.620
♪ kept apart by circumstance... ♪

70
00:04:21.320 --> 00:04:24.160
♪ will finally meet again! ♪

71
00:04:25.330 --> 00:04:27.710
♪ Under the moonlight... ♪

72
00:04:29.710 --> 00:04:31.250
So romantic!

73
00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:58.570
♪ ...their passion... ♪

74
00:04:59.150 --> 00:05:01.450
♪ burning! ♪

75
00:05:31.390 --> 00:05:32.520
Master Kin!

76
00:05:32.520 --> 00:05:33.440
Kin!

77
00:05:43.320 --> 00:05:46.160
I will avenge Lord Oden!

78
00:05:52.870 --> 00:05:55.040
Take this!

79
00:05:55.040 --> 00:05:57.920
You really wanna die that badly?

80
00:05:57.920 --> 00:06:00.420
Kin!

81
00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:26.870
What?!

82
00:06:39.210 --> 00:06:43.420
You guys are not Oden after all.

83
00:06:43.420 --> 00:06:47.550
Pretending to be great samurai
from the safety of Oden's shadow,

84
00:06:47.550 --> 00:06:52.430
and even now, after his death,
you still play at being samurai.

85
00:06:52.430 --> 00:06:54.060
What can you do?

86
00:06:54.060 --> 00:06:59.730
If you think we're just playing at being
samurai, why not fight us and find out?!

87
00:07:00.650 --> 00:07:03.530
All right... Bring it on!

88
00:07:03.530 --> 00:07:04.610
Attack!

89
00:07:23.210 --> 00:07:24.510
Crimson Cat Dance!

90
00:07:25.050 --> 00:07:27.010
Kappa Style...

91
00:07:31.310 --> 00:07:32.890
Celestial Torrent!

92
00:07:34.770 --> 00:07:35.640
What?!

93
00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:44.690
Canine Scourge!

94
00:07:47.570 --> 00:07:49.120
Lingering Snow Scythes!

95
00:07:54.500 --> 00:07:56.080
Slicing Rounds!

96
00:08:09.260 --> 00:08:10.930
What's this?!

97
00:08:10.930 --> 00:08:14.770
Their attacks aren't even close
to the level of Oden's swordplay.

98
00:08:14.770 --> 00:08:16.850
How can they cut me?!

99
00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:19.810
Kaido!

100
00:08:24.820 --> 00:08:26.490
Do it!

101
00:08:27.070 --> 00:08:29.240
I said, do it!

102
00:08:33.450 --> 00:08:36.000
Ninpo: Scroll-Scroll Technique!

103
00:08:46.090 --> 00:08:49.720
My scroll will roll up anything!

104
00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.070
And now, I return it to you...

105
00:09:06.070 --> 00:09:06.900
Blast Breath...

106
00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:08.820
Restoration!

107
00:09:46.400 --> 00:09:49.740
So you want to kill me?

108
00:09:50.070 --> 00:09:54.370
You're just a bunch of cowardly retainers...

109
00:09:54.370 --> 00:09:57.870
chasing your Lord Oden's phantom!

110
00:09:58.580 --> 00:10:00.040
He is right.

111
00:10:00.370 --> 00:10:02.250
We have always been cowards.

112
00:10:02.250 --> 00:10:05.540
I shall teach you how to use
the Oden two-sword style!

113
00:10:05.540 --> 00:10:07.550
No thank you.

114
00:10:07.550 --> 00:10:10.630
We possess our own style...

115
00:10:10.630 --> 00:10:14.180
But why?! This is the Oden two-sword style!

116
00:10:14.180 --> 00:10:16.930
Do you not want to inherit it?!

117
00:10:16.930 --> 00:10:18.930
Of course we wanted to inherit it.

118
00:10:19.390 --> 00:10:21.890
Everyone insisted they were his first disciple.

119
00:10:22.690 --> 00:10:26.440
There was a serious fight to determine
who was his first student.

120
00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:30.530
We all loved Oden so much,
it looked like a fight to the death.

121
00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:06.810
– Oden...
– Oden...

122
00:11:10.690 --> 00:11:12.940
– Two-Sword Style!
– Two-Sword Style!

123
00:11:12.940 --> 00:11:15.400
Is this your idea of a joke?

124
00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:20.080
Such pathetic imitations!

125
00:11:21.540 --> 00:11:23.370
Listen, guys!

126
00:11:23.370 --> 00:11:24.960
Ryuo is...

127
00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:29.840
Listen to me!

128
00:11:32.130 --> 00:11:37.510
We have honed our skills with the blade,
all for this day when we save Wano!

129
00:11:47.520 --> 00:11:49.520
Flame-Rend!

130
00:12:09.750 --> 00:12:14.800
Do not underestimate... my samurai!

131
00:12:15.340 --> 00:12:20.680
People will remember your
heroic death for generations.

132
00:12:21.180 --> 00:12:24.220
They can forget me for all I care!

133
00:12:24.220 --> 00:12:28.690
My spirit will live on!

134
00:12:29.230 --> 00:12:31.730
– Oden Two-Sword Style:
– Oden Two-Sword Style:

135
00:12:32.690 --> 00:12:37.150
– Halcyon Totsuka!
– Halcyon Totsuka!

136
00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:47.290
Hal

137
00:12:47.290 --> 00:12:47.500
Halcyon

138
00:12:47.370 --> 00:12:47.450
Totsu

139
00:12:47.450 --> 00:12:47.500
Totsuka

140
00:13:23.370 --> 00:13:28.290
Flower Capital

141
00:13:28.660 --> 00:13:31.290
Sing! Dance!

142
00:13:31.290 --> 00:13:34.880
Be merry! For today is the Fire Festival!

143
00:13:45.640 --> 00:13:50.270
The Flower Capital is the lone place
that flourishes in Wano.

144
00:13:50.980 --> 00:13:55.020
However, like the rest of the country,
its population hides terror and tension

145
00:13:55.020 --> 00:13:59.230
behind a thin veneer of frivolity.

146
00:14:00.190 --> 00:14:06.280
"Someday, the Kozuki samurai
will save this country."

147
00:14:07.660 --> 00:14:10.790
They could carry on...

148
00:14:10.790 --> 00:14:15.210
because they all believed
in such a seemingly true legend.

149
00:14:21.510 --> 00:14:22.760
Delicious!

150
00:14:22.760 --> 00:14:25.590
That really hits the spot!

151
00:14:26.140 --> 00:14:29.560
The Fire Festival sure is fun...

152
00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:31.430
Yes...

153
00:14:31.430 --> 00:14:33.770
It takes me back to the good old days.

154
00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:38.150
I wish today would go on just like this...

155
00:14:39.070 --> 00:14:41.650
forever and ever...

156
00:14:47.870 --> 00:14:49.580
So tasty!

157
00:14:50.040 --> 00:14:52.410
We get to drink such clean water.

158
00:14:52.410 --> 00:14:54.290
What a luxury!

159
00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:57.960
The air is so fresh...

160
00:14:57.960 --> 00:14:59.960
Let's really take it in.

161
00:15:01.090 --> 00:15:05.090
Once the festival ends, it's back to sobriety...

162
00:15:07.220 --> 00:15:09.470
for a whole 'nother year!

163
00:15:10.100 --> 00:15:11.180
Dammit!

164
00:15:12.310 --> 00:15:15.390
If only Orochi wasn't backed by Kaido!

165
00:15:15.390 --> 00:15:17.980
No one's gonna get killed today.

166
00:15:17.980 --> 00:15:20.230
What a wonderful day!

167
00:15:20.980 --> 00:15:24.400
Orochi will be back tomorrow, though!

168
00:15:29.870 --> 00:15:35.370
I bet the Kozuki Clan
is fighting them right now!

169
00:15:35.370 --> 00:15:38.580
Oh, that's interesting,
even if it's complete horseshit!

170
00:15:38.580 --> 00:15:40.290
Tell me more!

171
00:15:40.290 --> 00:15:45.420
Alright then! They've brought back
warriors from all over the world,

172
00:15:45.420 --> 00:15:51.560
and they're at Onigashima right now,
slicing up Orochi and Kaido and creating chaos!

173
00:15:52.560 --> 00:15:54.100
Keep going! Keep going!

174
00:15:54.100 --> 00:15:56.480
Today's the day to share wild fantasies!

175
00:16:14.410 --> 00:16:16.620
S-So cold...!

176
00:16:16.620 --> 00:16:18.670
Help me!

177
00:16:22.540 --> 00:16:23.550
This is bad...

178
00:16:23.550 --> 00:16:25.300
Stay away from them!

179
00:16:25.300 --> 00:16:26.800
Fall back!

180
00:16:27.420 --> 00:16:30.340
Get away from them!

181
00:16:36.140 --> 00:16:38.940
The samurai are splitting up... Why?

182
00:16:40.940 --> 00:16:43.150
This must be that plague of his...

183
00:16:43.150 --> 00:16:45.820
You'll turn into an ogre just by touching them.

184
00:16:45.820 --> 00:16:47.530
It's highly contagious...

185
00:16:47.530 --> 00:16:50.490
How could he spread such a virus?

186
00:16:50.990 --> 00:16:53.780
He's the real ogre here!

187
00:16:55.290 --> 00:16:57.960
Seal off the exits to the other floors!

188
00:16:57.960 --> 00:17:00.830
This floor is done for!

189
00:17:09.220 --> 00:17:12.510
This is my masterpiece!

190
00:17:13.140 --> 00:17:14.760
Plague rounds:

191
00:17:14.760 --> 00:17:16.640
Ice Ogre!

192
00:17:21.730 --> 00:17:23.980
1st Basement Level

Inside the Castle

193
00:17:21.810 --> 00:17:23.980
Outta my way!

194
00:17:24.400 --> 00:17:26.980
You damn cockroach!

195
00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:32.070
I said "Outta my way"!

196
00:17:33.120 --> 00:17:34.620
Wait, Luffy!

197
00:17:34.620 --> 00:17:35.950
What are you doing?!

198
00:17:36.330 --> 00:17:39.200
You're gonna fight Kaido, right?

199
00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:41.290
Save your energy for now!

200
00:17:41.290 --> 00:17:44.210
Off with Straw Hat's head!

201
00:17:44.210 --> 00:17:46.960
Outta the way, swirly brows!

202
00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:49.800
Let's do it!

203
00:17:49.800 --> 00:17:54.140
I can handle all of you brutes by myself!

204
00:17:59.730 --> 00:18:03.230
Party Table Kick Course!

205
00:18:19.240 --> 00:18:21.250
Damn you!

206
00:18:21.250 --> 00:18:23.960
How dare you do that to my men?!

207
00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:26.130
You're not getting past me!

208
00:18:27.880 --> 00:18:30.760
Prepare yourself!

209
00:18:30.760 --> 00:18:34.590
Headliner Briscola
Gorilla Smile Fruit
Beast Pirates

210
00:18:35.760 --> 00:18:38.350
Why's the gorilla growing
from there?! It's weird!

211
00:18:40.600 --> 00:18:42.730
Is that so?!

212
00:18:42.730 --> 00:18:46.400
Then how exactly should a gorilla...

213
00:18:48.900 --> 00:18:50.980
grow out of someone?!

214
00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:53.950
How would I know?!

215
00:18:56.530 --> 00:18:59.950
Gorilla Punch Punch!

216
00:19:01.080 --> 00:19:02.200
Wow!

217
00:19:02.200 --> 00:19:04.080
He's tougher than he looks!

218
00:19:04.080 --> 00:19:06.630
That Gorilla Punch is so cool!

219
00:19:12.050 --> 00:19:14.470
Water Shot!

220
00:19:23.680 --> 00:19:26.270
Oh! Jinbe!

221
00:19:36.150 --> 00:19:39.160
I thought I would find you around here.

222
00:19:39.160 --> 00:19:41.200
Looks like I was right...

223
00:19:41.740 --> 00:19:42.950
Briscola!

224
00:19:43.450 --> 00:19:44.870
Are you all right?

225
00:19:48.960 --> 00:19:50.590
Ow, ow, ow...

226
00:19:51.380 --> 00:19:53.300
Hey! Are you okay?!

227
00:19:53.300 --> 00:19:54.800
Stay with me!

228
00:20:01.470 --> 00:20:03.180
Hey, you!

229
00:20:03.180 --> 00:20:06.390
How dare you attack us!

230
00:20:06.770 --> 00:20:09.520
Alright! It's my turn now!

231
00:20:09.520 --> 00:20:14.480
Come on! How many times do I have
to tell you to save your energy?!

232
00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:17.490
You'll take too long beating up this many guys!

233
00:20:17.490 --> 00:20:18.450
Shut up!

234
00:20:18.450 --> 00:20:21.200
I'll polish them off in ten seconds!

235
00:20:21.200 --> 00:20:22.200
Any complaints?

236
00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:25.200
Yeah! It'd only take three
seconds if I was there!

237
00:20:26.330 --> 00:20:28.830
Hey, stop ignoring me!

238
00:20:28.830 --> 00:20:30.580
Prepare yourselves!

239
00:20:31.420 --> 00:20:35.760
Gorilla Punch Punch!

240
00:20:37.010 --> 00:20:41.260
Fishman Karate: Shark Tile Fist!

241
00:20:59.780 --> 00:21:02.370
Briscola!

242
00:21:06.750 --> 00:21:08.370
Oh, nice one!

243
00:21:08.370 --> 00:21:10.290
You're awesome, Jinbe!

244
00:21:10.290 --> 00:21:11.790
Luffy!

245
00:21:11.790 --> 00:21:14.170
I'll escort you to the rooftop!

246
00:21:14.170 --> 00:21:17.670
You need to save your energy for now!

247
00:21:17.670 --> 00:21:20.300
Why are you taking control?!

248
00:21:20.300 --> 00:21:22.840
I've already taken Luffy this far!

249
00:21:24.010 --> 00:21:26.140
I see. My apologies!

250
00:21:26.140 --> 00:21:30.230
Luffy! Our samurai allies
should be up there already!

251
00:21:30.230 --> 00:21:32.310
Let's meet up with them!

252
00:21:32.310 --> 00:21:34.110
Alright! Got it!

253
00:21:34.110 --> 00:21:36.440
How the hell are you so on top of everything?

254
00:21:36.440 --> 00:21:39.280
How dare you take down Briscola?!

255
00:21:39.280 --> 00:21:40.860
Get them!

