00:22:06.430 --> 00:22:07.890
Wait!

398
00:22:10.680 --> 00:22:12.940
What's the situation, Bao Huang?

399
00:22:12.940 --> 00:22:18.860
Right, so, Yamato and Momonosuke
are headed outside through the Right-Brain Tower!

400
00:22:18.860 --> 00:22:19.990
That's good enough.

401
00:22:22.030 --> 00:22:23.660
This is King.

402
00:22:23.660 --> 00:22:27.620
We've ascertained the identities of
the idiots who crashed the banquet.

403
00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:30.870
The enemy's army numbers around 5,400.

404
00:22:31.410 --> 00:22:36.210
The majority are samurai,
led by Oden's retainers.

405
00:22:37.210 --> 00:22:38.550
It would seem...

406
00:22:41.630 --> 00:22:44.590
the Kozuki Clan has staked its prestige...

407
00:22:44.590 --> 00:22:47.100
in an attempt to restore their name.

408
00:22:49.720 --> 00:22:56.610
They want to make Oden's son,
Kozuki Momonosuke, the shogun of Wano.

409
00:22:56.610 --> 00:23:00.110
To all available Gifters
and Soaring Six members...

410
00:23:00.110 --> 00:23:02.190
my orders are as follows:

411
00:23:03.900 --> 00:23:09.080
Kill Kozuki Momonosuke, who is currently
escaping through the Right-Brain Tower,

412
00:23:09.080 --> 00:23:11.240
and bring me his head!

413
00:23:11.240 --> 00:23:14.210
This will destroy the samurai's morale.

414
00:23:17.080 --> 00:23:23.050
Of course, I know the pirates
are another matter altogether.

415
00:23:33.730 --> 00:23:37.020
Our orders are to kill him,
not to bring him in...

416
00:23:37.020 --> 00:23:38.860
That makes things easier.

417
00:23:44.400 --> 00:23:45.360
Shoot.

418
00:23:59.580 --> 00:24:04.510
Armored Division
Beast Pirates

419
00:24:04.510 --> 00:24:06.550
Fetch me his corpse!

420
00:24:06.550 --> 00:24:07.550
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

421
00:24:10.050 --> 00:24:11.850
Here it is.

422
00:24:11.850 --> 00:24:13.970
Huh? What's this?

423
00:24:13.970 --> 00:24:14.890
A barrel?

424
00:24:26.490 --> 00:24:31.240
The Armored Division's defenses
cannot be broken by such a weapon!

425
00:24:38.920 --> 00:24:40.210
Shinobu!

426
00:24:40.210 --> 00:24:41.210
You mustn't!

427
00:24:41.210 --> 00:24:42.840
Please stay hidden!

428
00:24:44.880 --> 00:24:46.210
Nice try!

429
00:24:46.840 --> 00:24:50.800
Every member of our squad
has an armored body.

430
00:24:51.220 --> 00:24:53.390
There's no way out!

431
00:24:54.850 --> 00:24:56.390
Aim for the kid!

432
00:25:03.400 --> 00:25:05.110
Lord Momonosuke!

433
00:25:13.950 --> 00:25:16.290
Please... run...

434
00:25:17.620 --> 00:25:18.540
Shinobu...

435
00:25:20.830 --> 00:25:23.130
I'll kill you...

436
00:25:23.130 --> 00:25:24.920
along with the brat!

437
00:25:25.840 --> 00:25:27.630
You can't even shield him!

438
00:25:30.800 --> 00:25:31.970
Shinobu!

439
00:25:35.060 --> 00:25:36.930
Ru...

440
00:25:39.850 --> 00:25:42.900
Run, Lord Momonosuke!

441
00:25:43.310 --> 00:25:44.860
Run?

442
00:25:44.860 --> 00:25:48.780
Is that what a shogun is supposed to do?

443
00:25:54.660 --> 00:25:56.790
Shinobu! Shinobu!

444
00:25:57.990 --> 00:25:59.000
You're mine!

445
00:26:04.250 --> 00:26:05.500
I beg you...!

446
00:26:07.960 --> 00:26:11.630
I beg you!

447
00:26:41.160 --> 00:26:43.160
Well, well...

448
00:26:43.160 --> 00:26:45.130
Are you sure you want to interfere,

449
00:26:45.130 --> 00:26:46.790
Young Master Yamato?

450
00:26:48.550 --> 00:26:49.750
I'm not interfering.

451
00:26:50.760 --> 00:26:54.010
I'm here to fight for the Kozuki.

452
00:27:03.430 --> 00:27:06.560
For I... am Oden!

453
00:27:12.190 --> 00:27:14.150
Cut his throat!

454
00:27:14.150 --> 00:27:17.160
We haven't won until we've removed
his head from his neck!

455
00:27:17.160 --> 00:27:18.410
You are right!

456
00:27:18.410 --> 00:27:21.540
Sever Kaido's windpipe!

457
00:27:35.300 --> 00:27:41.220
Within your spirit, I saw
the shadow of Kozuki Oden...

458
00:27:42.180 --> 00:27:45.890
It wouldn't have been a bad death...

459
00:27:47.810 --> 00:27:50.020
Every time this scar aches,

460
00:27:50.020 --> 00:27:54.490
I remember that fateful day...

461
00:27:56.070 --> 00:27:57.160
Help!

462
00:28:00.450 --> 00:28:01.450
Father!

463
00:28:01.450 --> 00:28:04.250
Father, save me!

464
00:28:15.380 --> 00:28:16.760
Guess who!

465
00:28:23.890 --> 00:28:28.480
If only no one had interfered
at that exact moment...

466
00:28:29.900 --> 00:28:34.440
But you guys are not Oden after all...

467
00:28:41.700 --> 00:28:47.210
There will never be another
monstrous samurai like him!

468
00:28:48.290 --> 00:28:50.330
It's too shallow!

469
00:28:50.330 --> 00:28:56.050
You aren't even strong enough
to reopen the old scar!

470
00:28:59.430 --> 00:29:02.220
None of you are!

471
00:29:19.030 --> 00:29:20.320
Invisible slashes?!

472
00:29:40.930 --> 00:29:42.010
– Kiku!
– Kiku!
